posting_body: ['Arterra', '711 West Casino Rd, Everett, WA, 98204', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 10', 'OR Text', '10', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'Welcome Home to Arterra', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 720 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to Arterra, a gorgeously landscaped community in Everett, WA offering newly renovated apartments and fabulous amenities.', 'Feel at home in a spacious, open-concept one or two bedroom apartment with nine-foot ceilings.', 'Gorgeous hardwood-style flooring and sleek stainless steel appliances in select homes will impress your guests.', 'Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace or entertain your friends on your very own patio or balcony.', 'Laundry rooms, built-in desks and large closets ensure a convenient living experience.', 'Speak with the leasing team today to learn more.', 'Features', '- Large Closets', '- Ceiling Fan', '- Garbage Disposals', '- Patio or Balcony', '- Renovated Homes**', '- Cable & Internet Ready', '- Wood Burning Fireplaces', '- Hardwood-Style Flooring*', '- Stainless Steel Appliances*', '- Washer & Dryer in Unit', '*In Select Units', 'Community Amenities', '- Outdoor Fire Pit', '- Dog Park', '- Near Public Transportation', '- Covered Parking', '- Easy Access to I5 & I405', '- Playground', '- Courtyard', '- BBQ & Picnic Area', '- Business Center', '- Clubhouse', '- Onsite Maintenance', '- Onsite Management', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Arterra welcomes your pet!', 'Our apartments accommodate up to two pets per home, with no weight limit.', 'There is a $300 Pet Fee and Pet Deposit of $300.', 'Pet Rent is $30.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Please call our leasing office for complete Pet Policy.', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'UC6gJdcF0']
